trans-unit.source: Acts as the top of a two-level named hierarchy of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection" /> collections.
trans-unit.target: Funciona como a parte superior de uma hierarquia nomeada de dois níveis de coleções <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection> class is both a root-level <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collection and a container for a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Configuration.RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection> classe é ambos um nível raiz <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> coleção e um contêiner para um <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> coleção.

trans-unit.source: These collections allow you to create named groups of more <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collections, each containing individual named <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objects.
trans-unit.target: Essas coleções permitem que você crie grupos de mais nomeados <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> coleções, cada indivíduo recipiente nomeado <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objetos.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the profile features added to [!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)], see [NIB: ASP.NET Profile Properties](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/06a7bf4a-a5a2-462d-9793-c79063a2018d).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre os recursos de perfil adicionada ao [!INCLUDE[vstecasplong](~/includes/vstecasplong-md.md)], consulte [NIB: propriedades de perfil ASP.NET](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/06a7bf4a-a5a2-462d-9793-c79063a2018d).
